text: Theunis van Wyk (born 21 March 1944) is a Zambian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle middleweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Zambian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Northern Rhodesia Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
